spec_data.Name: python-ceph-compat
spec_data.License: LGPL-2.1 and CC-BY-SA-1.0 and GPL-2.0 and BSL-1.0 and BSD-3-Clause and MIT
spec_data.Description:
This is a compatibility package to accommodate python-ceph split into
python-rados, python-rbd, python-rgw and python-cephfs. Packages still
depending on python-ceph should be fixed to depend on python-rados,
python-rbd, python-rgw or python-cephfs instead.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 01 Oct 2017 08:17:41 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Compatibility package for Cephs python libraries
